77.2	Hiro_Nakamura	Hiro Nakamura	Hiro Nakamura Nakamura Hiro) is a fictional character on the NBC fantasy drama Heroes who possesses the ability of space-time manipulation. This means that Hiro is able to alter the flow of time. Previously, his ability allowed him to teleport, stop time, or travel through time, but recent events in the series have prevented him from regaining his full abilities. He is played by Japanese-American actor Masi Oka.	http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/en/thumb/6/61/Ando_Hiro_ECT.jpg/250px-Ando_Hiro_ECT.jpg
